        <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          In <strong>{cityData.City}</strong>, the local environment demands a specialized approach to arboriculture. {cityData.Description}
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: #4b5563;">
